name: New Friend, New Home
description:
Raka said "The cat looks like a cat left behind from its owner".

Rai accidentally remembered when on the bus the cat was sitting in front of them. After they discussed Rai & Raka tried to follow the cat, the cat took them to a house.

Raka knocked on the door, there were 2 children behind the door.
It turns out that they are the owner of the cute black cat, a boy wearing a cute hat and his little sister who looks happy that her beloved cat is back.

At that time Raka accidentally read a sign written across the street, the sign says "For Rent". Finally after a long journey and their efforts to find a new place to live, Rai & Raka find that hope is in front of their eyes.

That house became the beginning of Rai & Raka are friends with them and
Their meeting will be a new journey for adventure together.

* This description was translated using google translate
